            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Where can I find neovim log files to find what caused the crash?\n\nIf it crashed then it doesn't have a chance to log, usually.\n\nWe have docs for [getting a backtrace](https://neovim.io/doc/user/dev_tools.html#dev-tools-backtrace) but missing steps for Windows. \n\nTo get a backtrace on Windows, here is what chatgpt says: https://chatgpt.com/share/68ceee3c-b328-8004-a2cb-8cce4e0849f4\n\nIf you find steps that work, let me know and I will update our docs.",
